CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775135469
OL,3,CDetectives investigating teenager's
OL,4,Cmurder issue plea for video shared
OL,5,Conline
OL,7,FWest Yorkshire Police are appealing
OL,8,Ffor footage which they believe "may be
OL,9,Fbeing shared on Tiktok or Snapchat,
OL,10,Fwill lead to the truth about what
OL,11,Fhappened".
OL,13,FSenior Investigating Officer Detective
OL,14,FChief Inspector James Entwistle, said:
OL,15,F"We have seen the impact that Chloe's
OL,16,Fdeath has had ` not just on her family
OL,17,Fand friends, but also across our
OL,18,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775135469
OL,3,CDetectives investigating teenager's
OL,4,Cmurder issue plea for video shared
OL,5,Conline
OL,7,F"While we have so far charged three
OL,8,Fpeople with her murder, this is very
OL,9,Fmuch an ongoing investigation, and we
OL,10,Fare committed to bringing all those
OL,11,Fresponsible for causing Chloe's death
OL,12,Fto justice.
OL,14,FA total of six people have been
OL,15,Farrested in connection with the
OL,16,Finvestigation so far.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
