PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775135469
OL,3,CDetectives investigating teenager's
OL,4,Cmurder issue plea for video shared
OL,5,Conline
OL,7,FAn 18-year-old man from Leeds who was
OL,8,Farrested on Tuesday 31 March, on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of murder has been released
OL,10,Fon bail pending further enquiries,
OL,11,Falong with an 18-year-old woman and a
OL,12,F17-year-old boy who were arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of murder last Saturday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
