OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775135469
OL,3,CDetectives investigating teenager's
OL,4,Cmurder issue plea for video shared
OL,5,Conline
OL,7,FKayla Smith, aged 18, and Archie
OL,8,FRycroft, aged 19, who have been
OL,9,Fcharged with Chloe's murder, have been
OL,10,Fremanded in custody to appear before
OL,11,FLeeds Crown Court tomorrow, Thursday 2
OL,12,FApril, along with a 17-year-old boy
OL,13,Ffrom Leeds who cannot be named for
OL,14,Flegal reasons.
OL,16,FWest Yorkshire Police are appealing
OL,17,Fwith anyone information, or anyone who
OL,18,Fhas the footage to come forward.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
